import React from 'react'
import { Text, TextInput , view, Button } from 'react-native'

export default function Form () {
  
    return (

    
      <View>
            <View>
                 <Text>Altura</Text>
                 <TextInput 
                 
                 placeholder='Ex, 1.71'
                 keyboardType='numeric'
                 
                 />

                 <Text>Peso</Text>
                 <TextInput
                   placeholder='Ex, 65.365'
                   keyboardType='numeric'

                 />
           </View> 
      </View>

    );
  }
